Description:
Single-Level Sensation in the Best Location!
*Due to Melbourne's Stage 4 Restrictions, all Nelson Alexander team members are working from home. Please contact us via email or phone to speak about your options to view this property virtually. Thank you.*
Unit 2 & 4 NOW SOLD - ONLY 1 remaining!!
Brand-new and ready to simply move in and enjoy, this brilliant rear villa presents a lifestyle opportunity of low-maintenance perfection with its intelligent design, quality inclusions and premier position in a sought-after Niddrie-edge neighbourhood. Every room filled with natural light, the free-flowing interior showcases two bedrooms (larger master) both with mirrored robes, along with a stylish central bathroom complete with separate shower and bathtub. The versatility of the open-plan living/dining area is matched by the quality of the kitchen boasting stone benchtops and island breakfast bar, soft-close drawers and Technika appliances (dishwasher, oven and gas cooktop). Other stand-out features include split-system heating and cooling (living area and both bedrooms), square-set ceilings with efficient LED lighting, quality carpets and engineered floors, concealed laundry facilities and double-glazed windows all-round. Step outside to discover a wonderfully wide rear courtyard plus the added appeal of a remote-control garage with internal entry. A short stroll to Matthews Avenue trams, Keilor Road's renowned cafes, restaurants and retail precinct, close to primary and secondary schools, as well as easy access to Essendon Fields Shopping Centre and the Tullamarine Freeway/Citylink.

Whether you're a first home buyer or investor, this wonder home makes for a perfect starting point. Situated in a quiet area of Albanvale close to Diamond Reserve and Albanvale Primary School, public transport and Brimbank Shopping Centre. This home comprises three bedrooms with built in robes, bright spacious lounge, well equipped kitchen with adjoining meals area with split system, large outdoor entertainment area with pergola, storage shed, 2nd living zone with toilet and shower or you can convert into a garage.

Description:
Immediate comfort and family appeal
In a great location, close to Milleara Shopping Centre, Parklands and schools, this single level three bedroom brick home offers family flexibility. An immaculate layout comprises an inviting entry flowing to stylish living/dining zones. The Tasmanian Oak kitchen with adjoining family room gives you multiple living zones and space for a growing family. Elegantly serving three robed bedrooms is a pristine bathroom, flaunting spa bath, vanity and shower. An in-ground solar heated pool amidst private landscaped gardens, a side drive to assure great car accommodation and an alluring alfresco allows you to continue the family's fun. Complemented by split-system air conditioner, gas log fire, ceiling fans, polished Tassie Oak floorboards and garden shed. Walking distance to St Peters Primary, Milleara Shopping Centre, parklands, buses and freeways. Land 679m2 (approx.).
Inspection by Appointment Only

Description:
Unique Signature Style
With the health and wellbeing of our community being front of mind we have additional measures in place at all property inspections. Our COVID-19 conditions of entry are available for your viewing click here: https://go.aws/2Z5oMmV
With an unwavering dedication to exemplary family living and entertaining, this comprehensively modernised, one-of-a-kind four bedroom, two bathroom plus study single storey residence delivers an environment of absolute renovation perfection. Making a bold first impression, an impeccably presented living zone features soaring ceilings, clerestory windows and epoxy-resin floors. Further along, a spacious open dining zone flows to a brilliantly executed, fully enclosed entertaining/dining area, showcasing Merbau decking, Velux skylights, fully integrated mains gas barbeque, wine fridge and custom-made blinds, overlooking a solar-heated/salt-chlorinated inground pool/spa. Showcasing Caesarstone benchtops, premium 2-pac cabinetry, stainless steel freestanding cooker, dishwasher, cutting edge tiled splashbacks and servery window, the kitchen is stunning. Beautiful accommodation comprises master with walk-in-robe and designer ensuite. A gorgeous main bathroom, with rainfall shower, bathtub and porcelain floor-to-ceiling tiles, serves additional bedrooms. Poolside shower, low maintenance landscaped surrounds, BIRS, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, alarm/CCTV, automated double garage. Close to Taylors Lakes Secondary College, primary schools, Watergardens Shopping Centre, train station, parklands, buses and freeways.

Description:
As-New Lifestyle of Light and Luxury
Please register your interest in this property so that we can ensure you are included in the Virtual Auction and/or contacted in the event the property is going to be sold prior to the Virtual Auction 7th August at 12pm
*** This property is available for inspection by appointment - Please contact us to arrange a suitable time ***
This single-level sensation (c2019) is set to impress with its intelligent design, first-class features throughout and established garden surrounds providing a perfect environment of easy-living excellence along with immediate access to the best of Keilor East. Bathed in northerly light, the home's meticulously detailed interior showcases three bedrooms (large master with fitted WIR), opulent ensuite and equally-stylish main bathroom - both with stone-top vanities and floor-to-ceiling tiles. Adding to its versatility is a study area/sitting room and spacious open-plan living/dining area complemented by a superb stone-bench kitchen complete with ample cupboards space and walk-in pantry, Bosch dishwasher and 900mm cooking appliances. High square-set ceilings throughout, the home also includes ducted heating and refrigerated cooling, alarm and video intercom, solid hardwood floors, double blinds, full-size laundry and large linen cupboards. Double sliding doors from the living area reveal a sunny courtyard with large entertaining deck and established perimeter gardens, plus the added appeal of an internally-accessed garage (remote-control) and additional driveway parking. Woorite Place buses at the end of the street and walking distance to Centreway shops and cafes, it's also close to primary and secondary schools (including PEGS), Steele Creek trails and parkland as well as easy access to the Calder Freeway.

Description:
Delightful Family Living In a Premier Location!
Immaculate presentation, attractive outdoor dimensions and incredible convenience give this delightful home an instant appeal. Positioned in a highly sought-after location (500m (approx.) from Burnside Heights and Taylors Hill), this superb family home provides maximum comfort inside and out with the bonus of privacy and security once you close your front door. Upon entrance, you will discover an instantly inviting lounge and dining area, a well-appointed kitchen with updated appliances and ample storage space overlooks the casual living zone perfect for the growing family. The master bedroom includes a modern ensuite and walk in robe with a further 2 bedrooms sharing the modern family bathroom. An impressively scaled pergola area extends the family domain outdoors whilst the large sun-drenched garden provides plenty of room for the whole family to enjoy.
Positioned on 531sqm of land, this home is full of features including ducted heating, roller shutters, separate full-sized laundry, large enclosed storage space which has the potential to be turned in to a garage and roller door with side access to the rear. A prized location merely moments away from Gilson College, local schools, public transport and open parkland. This is family living at its absolute best!!

Description:
Superb Spaces in a Family Location!
This spacious family home in a popular neighbourhood presents a great lifestyle opportunity. The combination of comfort & impressive proportions culminate in a home that offers both formal and informal living spaces, perfect for all families.
The inviting interior comprises a large formal lounge. Flowing on from the lounge room is the timber kitchen with butlers pantry adjoining meals area. Sitting on approximately 541m2 of land and situated in a superb pocket of Kings Park within walking distance to schools, shops, parks, sporting fields, public transport and major amenities. This well-kept home is sure to impress upon inspection.

Description:
Modern Oasis of Luxury and Location!
***This property is available for inspection by appointment - Please contact us to arrange a suitable time***
In a sought-after Niddrie-edge neighbourhood, this rear townhouse (c2016) delivers a lifestyle of low-maintenance perfection with its intelligent design, premium inclusions and secluded surrounds - an ideal choice for professionals and downsizers alike. High square-set ceilings throughout, the home's beautifully-appointed interior showcases a large downstairs master bedroom with WIR, two additional bedrooms with BIRs (upstairs) and two on-trend bathrooms - one on each level. Bathed in natural light, the versatile open-plan living/dining area as accompanied by a superb stone-bench kitchen complete with soft-close cabinetry, feature tiled splashbacks, Baumatic cooking appliances and dishwasher. Other highlights of this remarkable residence include split-system heating and cooling (both levels), alarm and video intercom, plantation shutters, quality flooring, concealed laundry facilities and excellent storage options. Step outside to discover a sunny courtyard with northerly aspect, entertaining deck and high fences for privacy, plus the added appeal of a remote-control garage and additional parking space on title. Walking distance to Matthews Avenue trams, Keilor Road cafes/restaurants and shopping precinct, primary and secondary schools, as well as easy access to Essendon Fields Shopping Centre and freeway/Citylink.
*** COVID-19 Announcement ***
If you're attending an open for inspection, we request that you only attend if you are fit and healthy to do so and not under any self-isolation conditions. We request that you maintain a healthy distance from anyone attending the open for inspection, including other prospective buyers and our team members, and if requested wait outside so as to reduce the number of people in the property at any one time. Lastly, please refrain from touching items/fixtures and doors within the properties. If you would like to view something in particular, please request the agent's assistance. Thank you.

Description:
Sensational Style, Perfectly Positioned!
Please also register your interest to attend the auction so that we can ensure compliance with the latest regulations and be contacted in the event the property is going to be sold prior.
Moments from the buzz of Centreway in the very heart of Keilor East, this modern side-by-side residence delivers a lifestyle of low-maintenance perfection with its floorplan flexibility, long list of features and terrific living/entertaining spaces both inside and out. Beautifully appointed, the home's immaculate interior comprises three main bedrooms (extra-large master with WIR and private ensuite), along with a study/home office (or fourth bedroom), stylish central bathroom and guest powder room (third WC). Adding to its versatility is a separate lounge and spacious open-plan living/dining area with motorised blinds accompanied by a stone-bench kitchen with breakfast bar, ample cupboard space, stainless steel cooking appliances and Asko dishwasher. Along with split-system heating/cooling throughout and plantation shutters all-round, the home also features a comprehensive security system (alarm, CCTV and video intercom), solid hardwood floors, full-size laundry and under-stair storeroom. Stacker doors (from the living area) reveal an expansive outdoor entertainers' deck complete with retractable awning (remote controlled/wind sensing) and high fences for added privacy, plus two handy garden sheds, internally-accessed garage and additional driveway parking. Walking distance to shops and cafes, Milleara Road buses along with a range of primary and secondary schools (including PEGS), it's also close to Steele Creek trails and acres of parkland as well as easy access to the Calder Freeway.
*** COVID-19 Announcement ***
If you're attending an open for inspection, we request that you only attend if you are fit and healthy to do so and not under any self-isolation conditions. We request that you maintain a healthy distance from anyone attending the open for inspection, including other prospective buyers and our team members, and if requested wait outside so as to reduce the number of people in the property at any one time. Lastly, please refrain from touching items/fixtures and doors within the properties. If you would like to view something in particular, please request the agent's assistance. Thank you.
